95
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:19,520
You wanted to save
Shangguan Yan back then, not me

96
00:06:19,520 --> 00:06:21,600
You set me up?

97
00:06:33,320 --> 00:06:36,120
(I was supposed
to keep a distance from that jinx.)

98
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:38,720
(But I'm trapped now.)

99
00:06:39,400 --> 00:06:42,360
(I'll be tormented before leaving.)

100
00:06:53,200 --> 00:06:55,520
(I can't stand it.)

101
00:06:56,640 --> 00:06:57,640
(Forget it.)

102
00:07:00,755 --> 00:07:04,412
♪Time has taken away all
between you and me♪

103
00:07:04,412 --> 00:07:06,524
♪Yet memories surreptitiously remain♪

104
00:07:06,524 --> 00:07:09,177
