105
00:07:09,497 --> 00:07:12,569
♪Is but an exchange of glances
in a split second♪

106
00:07:12,921 --> 00:07:16,921
♪The stars that light up the night
scattered around us♪

107
00:07:16,921 --> 00:07:21,372
♪So-called worries become
an excuse to evade♪

108
00:07:21,372 --> 00:07:23,871
♪Not daring to look back again♪

109
00:07:24,313 --> 00:07:28,825
♪Your tenderness is always behind me♪

